      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. You seem to be heavily weighting the racial demographics in your assessment of stability. Can you explain the specific correlation you're seeing between the racial makeup of these neighborhoods and their \"risk\" level? Why does a higher percentage of Black or Hispanic residents automatically translate to higher instability for a commercial investor?",
